<br />
<br />It's funny you mention this, because I do exactly what you're saying with the 2 screens. I have 1 visible screen, and then the two invisible halves on opposite sides. So I guess it still is possible. But then again, in my situation I won't go back and change anything because my metatile system happens to work quite nicely (and without a lot of complexity).
